{"tid":1360240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一群經濟日報集團員工致香港人公開信","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:33:08.000Z","uid":9958,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4547fca95f9eea6af0c1003887a181154719e4a4","tid":1360240,"uid":9958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"致香港人<br />\n<br />\n作為經濟日報集團員工，我們絕不接受石鏡泉先生於7月22日所發出的道歉聲明，並強烈反對石鏡泉先生再於經濟日報集團旗下平台發布任何文章，以免影響員工士氣。<br />\n<br />\n對於石鏡泉先生於7月20日所發表的「藤條教仔論」，香港人定必追究到底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一群經濟日報集團員工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPcsZQ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPcsZQ5.png&h=21305b96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02ed9f1d944c14d8e04b543fc58e484c885cce52","tid":1360240,"uid":59699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n政府立即回應五大訴求"},{"pid":"2485d9bc7a0d24ae83e22aed9dd27526f4531843","tid":1360240,"uid":279866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:37:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"df079f7a5730bd8e4d4f731cea936f13f0bdf2a8","tid":1360240,"uid":9958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ac5dc0a68a365bcae9208a462db7544229c22c3","tid":1360240,"uid":138296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"},{"pid":"92353f93622a18eeac483ce6699ad8522934260b","tid":1360240,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團<br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"839e85de1840393589df3736b61ec5c421457384","tid":1360240,"uid":133435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"pus"},{"pid":"b620a7a417e5b0d7880e1ccd2